Expression Conditional Tests
============================

Simple if-then-else:
Check 10>5: {{@if intvalue10 > 5 then "yes" else "no"}}
Check 2>5: {{@if intvalue2 > 5 then "yes" else "no"}}

With calculations:
Sum check: {{@if intvalue10 + intvalue2 > 10 then "big" else "small"}}
Product check: {{@if intvalue2 * intvalue1 > 5 then "large" else "tiny"}}

Nested conditionals:
Nested: {{@if intvalue10 > 5 then (if intvalue2 > 1 then "A" else "B") else "C"}}

Boolean expressions:
And: {{@if intvalue10 > 5 and intvalue2 > 1 then "both" else "not both"}}
Or: {{@if intvalue10 < 5 or intvalue2 > 1 then "one true" else "none"}}

Comparison operators:
Equal: {{@if intvalue10 = 10 then "equal" else "not equal"}}
Not equal: {{@if intvalue10 <> 5 then "different" else "same"}}
GTE: {{@if intvalue10 >= 10 then "gte" else "lt"}}
LTE: {{@if intvalue2 <= 2 then "lte" else "gt"}}
